{
  "stem": "19518.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, and somehow in a mysterious way, in an unknown way, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was all alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was all alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I explained to them I was in a valley, deep in a valley, and this-- with big fir trees reaching the sky.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Behind me was a building like a sukkah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the only way I could describe it, like a sukkah that you build for the holiday Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it had windows, and it was painted green.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I smelled lilac that was May.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I smelled lilac.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And my father says to me, my god, what a dream.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my dream came true exactly, to the trees and to the barrack, and to the month of May.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have sometimes premonitions, and I hate myself for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband died one month short of 48 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I hope he's in-- with peace now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It affected us all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I try to be a good mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But like my daughter said lately, something-- we grew up in a home where there were always people, but no relatives.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOBBING] It had effect on my children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to spend sometimes hours during the night standing by the baby's crib, listening if the baby's still alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] [SIGHS] The nightmares that I had, and that included my children, were real nightmares that I just couldn't come out of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Life is very depressing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you have no one to speak to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is nobody you could talk to, nobody that could understand it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People that went through the same thing that I did, naturally if we get together, we have someone to talk to.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
